== Description ==

MMM (MySQL Master-Master Replication Manager) is set of flexible scripts 
to perform monitoring and management of MySQL Masrter-Master replication 
cluster configurations.

== Links ==

Project page on Google Code: http://code.google.com/p/mysql-master-master/

== Documentation ==

Currently documentation is being created on author's site and does not packaged 
in source tree snapshots or releases.

Most recent documentation could be found in project's wiki:
http://code.google.com/p/mysql-master-master/w/list

